name: Bitcoin Pizza 80331
description: This NFT entitles the owner to claim the Bitcoin Pizza #80331 (InscriptionID: 42ce93e269f13aebf94845d2c46a02433ea8ed19e217e770c78294e1b23f42d3i0) inscribed on the Bitcoin Blockchain. Ordinals are digital assets inscribed on Satoshis, the lowest denomination of Bitcoin (BTC). Please open a Support Ticket in our Discord to Claim the Pizza. In order to claim the Ordinal, a compatible Bitcoin address is required. Please follow this Tutorial to Setup a compatible Bitcoin Wallet: https://docs.raredough.com/receiving-bitcoin-ordinals
